title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table with highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export process should proceed without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export data from a table that contains a highlight/map.
3. Observe the exception thrown during the export process.
